# Environment Variables Example
# Copy this file to create your own .env file (which is ignored by git)

# Gemini AI API Key (Optional - for AI-generated stories)
# Get your key at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/api-keys
# If not set, the app will use template-based stories
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# Note: This is just an example file.
# For local development, create a file named 'gemini_api_key' in the project root
# and add your API key there. That file is already in .gitignore.

# For CI/CD environments, set environment variables directly:
# - GitHub Actions: Use repository secrets
# - GitHub Codespaces: Use repository codespace secrets
# - Local: export GEMINI_API_KEY='your_key' && flutter run --dart-define=GEMINI_API_KEY=$GEMINI_API_KEY
